SQL_STMT_U.val: select US_UUS_ID, RT_URT_KEY, RT_NAME from :1 u, :2 r where r.RT_RECHTBRON = 'DOC_TEMP' and u.us_uus_id between ':6' and ':7' and not exists (select 1 from :3 ur where ur.UR_UUS_ID = u.US_UUS_ID and ur.UR_URT_KEY = r.RT_URT_KEY) and not exists (select 1 from :4 g, :5 gr where g.UG_UUS_ID = u.US_UUS_ID and gr.GR_UGP_NAME = g.UG_UGP_NAME and gr.GR_URT_KEY = r.RT_URT_KEY) ORDER BY US_UUS_ID asc, RT_URT_KEY asc

Text.valUnicode: RAPPORTAGE NIET TOEGEKENDE RECHTEN PER GEBRUIKER

ExpSyntax.val: IF({1,14},'<Het rapport is afgebroken door de gebruiker>.','<EINDE RAPPORT>')
